CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 3, 1952, pg. 20 reads: "Neighborhood Unit Conference - Participating in seventh annual conference of the units were the Rev. Leroy Patrick, Mrs. Ethel Sutton, Gaines T. Bradford, Mrs. Eunity Howard, Alexander J. Allen, Mrs. Elizabeth C. Johnson, Thomas E. Barton, R. Maurice Moss, the principal speaker at the dinner meeting; the Rev. Samuel D. Rudder, presiding; J.C.F. Motz, Mrs. Lula B. Providence and the Rev. and Mrs. Virgil Moccia. - Harris Photo"
TitMainTitle: Group portrait, left to right: Rev. Leroy Patrick, Ethel Sutton, Gaines T. Bradford, Eunity Howard, Alexander J. Allen, Elizabeth C. Johnson, Thomas E. Barton, R. Maurice Moss, Rev. Samuel D. Rudder, J.C.F. Motz, Lula B. Providence, and the Rev. and Mrs. Virgil Moccia, seated at long banquet table, in interior with huge banner that reads "Urban League of Pittsburgh... National Urban League... American Teamwork Works... and Interracial Teamwork in Action"
